Package co.cask.cdap.api.templates

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AdapterConfigurer
    Configurer used to configure program used in the execution of the Adapter.
    AdapterContext
    Provides access to template adapter context when a program is executing as an adapter.
    AdapterPluginRegistry
    This interface provides method to register plugin usage for an adapter.
    AdapterSpecification
    Specification of an adapter.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ApplicationTemplate<T>
    An ApplicationTemplate is a special type of Application that can be given a configuration object to create an application instance.
